<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BharatVote - Secure Online Voting</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/index.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/feather-icons/dist/feather.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/feather-icons"></script>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600&family=Noto+Sans+Devanagari:wght@400;500&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Hind:wght@600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container header-container">
            <div class="logo">
                <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48">
                    <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="21" fill="#138808" />
                    <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="16" fill="#FFFFFF" />
                    <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="11" fill="#138808" />
                </svg>
                <span>Bharat<span class="highlight">Vote</span></span>
            </div>

            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/dashboard">Vote</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/result">Results</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>

            <% if(userId){ %>
                <div class="nav-buttons">
                    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary">Dashboard</a>
                    <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-outline">Logout</a>
                </div>
                <% }else{ %>
                    <div class="nav-buttons">
                        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-outline">Login</a>
                        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">Register</a>
                    </div>
                    <% } %>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container hero-content">
            <h1>Secure Digital Democracy for Every Indian</h1>
            <p>Empowering citizens with a transparent, accessible, and trustworthy online voting platform. Your vote,
                your voice - safeguarded with cutting-edge technology and uncompromising integrity.</p>
            <% if(userId){ %>
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary">Go to Dashboard</a>
                </div>
                <% }else{ %>
                    <div class="cta-buttons">
                        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">Register to Vote</a>
                        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-secondary">Login to Platform</a>
                    </div>
                    <% } %>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Why Choose Bharat Vote ?</h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card secure">
                    <div class="feature-icon">üîí</div>
                    <h3>Military-Grade Security</h3>
                    <p>Our platform use multi-factor authentication to ensure your vote remains confidential and
                        tamper-proof.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card transparent">
                    <div class="feature-icon">üëÅÔ∏è</div>
                    <h3>Complete Transparency</h3>
                    <p>Verifiable audit trails and open-source protocols allow public oversight while maintaining voter
                        anonymity and electoral integrity.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card easy">
                    <div class="feature-icon">üì±</div>
                    <h3>Accessible to All</h3>
                    <p>Designed for simplicity with multilingual support and accessibility features, ensuring every
                        eligible Indian can participate effortlessly.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Ready to Shape India's Future?</h2>
            <p>Join millions of empowered citizens casting their votes securely from anywhere. Register today and be
                part of the digital democracy revolution.</p>
            <div class="cta-buttons light" style="display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 1rem;">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-grid">
                <div class="footer-col">
                    <h3>BharatVote</h3>
                    <p>India's premier online voting platform. Making democracy accessible, secure, and transparent for
                        every Indian citizen.</p>
                    <div class="social-links">
                        <a href="#"><i data-feather="facebook"></i></a>
                        <a href="#"><i data-feather="twitter"></i></a>
                        <a href="#"><i data-feather="instagram"></i></a>
                        <a href="#"><i data-feather="linkedin"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-col">
                    <h3>Contact Us</h3>
                    <div class="contact-info">
                        <i data-feather="mail"></i>
                        <span>support@Bharatvote.in</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-info">
                        <i data-feather="phone"></i>
                        <span>011-2345-6789</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-info">
                        <i data-feather="map-pin"></i>
                        <span>Electoral Commission Building, New Delhi</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="copyright">
                <p>¬© 2023 BharatVote. Created by the Election Commission of India. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        feather.replace();
    </script>
</body>

</html>